  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Accuracy
    A standard accuracy provider.
    EpochAction<T>  
    Evaluation
    An evaluation metric provider for models.
    Evaluator
    A single evaluator metric provider.
    MLContextProvider
    A context provider for a machine learning context.
    Model
    Model - A model that can be saved, loaded, deployed, and evaluated.
    ModelConvertible<M extends Model>
    A model convertible represents a class that can be converted to a storable model.
    ParallelModelTrainer
    A parallel model trainer which provides a parallel training interface for models.
    Predictable
    A predictable model is a model that can be used to predict an output from an input.
    Trainable
    A trainable model is a model that can be trained on a data set.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivationFunction
    An activation function which is applied to the output of a neuron to determine its output.
    ActivationFunctionSerializer  
    IterableTimeEstimator
    An iterable time estimator which estimates the time remaining for a given number of epochs.
    ModelArchive
    A shared tool for saving models to a directory.
    ModelLoader
    A flexible model loader for machine learning models.
    ModelMetrics
    A common model evaluation metric provider, providing the following metrics: Accuracy Precision Recall F1 Score Call ModelMetrics.evaluate() to calculate the metrics.
    ModelRemapper
    A model conversion which provides a remapper for name, saving, and versioning.
    ModelRemapperBuilder
    Builder class for ModelRemapper.
    ParallelModelTrainers
    A parallel model trainer which provides multithreaded training for models.
